open bidding going

00:35:13.200 --> 00:35:15.450
to drive higher revenue
because everyone's

00:35:15.450 --> 00:35:17.340
competing for each
of those users

00:35:17.340 --> 00:35:19.480
on a real-time,
one-by-one basis,

00:35:19.480 --> 00:35:23.520
but it's also going to decrease
a lot of the extra time

00:35:23.520 --> 00:35:26.670
